    <item>
      <title>马来西亚 2025 年支出计划有望吸引外国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/malaysia-s-2025-spending-plan-poised-to-draw-foreign-interest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着马来西亚政府继续推进财政改革，创纪录的支出计划将进一步推动外国对其资产的兴趣，即使对股市的直接影响不大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/malaysia-s-2025-spending-plan-poised-to-draw-foreign-interest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:44:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国银行大幅下调贷款利率以提振疲弱经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/chinese-banks-slash-key-lending-rates-to-bolster-ailing-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为旨在恢复经济增长和阻止房地产市场崩溃的一系列措施之一，中国央行在 9 月底降低了基准贷款利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/chinese-banks-slash-key-lending-rates-to-bolster-ailing-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 01:01:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南总理预计 2025 年经济增长率将达到 6.5% 至 7%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/vietnam-premier-chinh-sees-2025-economic-growth-at-6-5-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据越南政府网站报道，越南总理范明政预计，2025 年越南经济将增长 6.5% 至 7%，并表示政府将推动经济扩张至 7% 至 7.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/vietnam-premier-chinh-sees-2025-economic-growth-at-6-5-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 00:52:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>24 亿美元流入 ETF 后，比特币价格逼近 7 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/bitcoin-btc-flirts-with-70-000-after-2-4-billion-inflow-into-etfs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于大量资金流入比特币这种最大数字资产的交易所交易基金 (ETF)，以及对美国监管前景的乐观情绪提振了市场人气，比特币周一走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/bitcoin-btc-flirts-with-70-000-after-2-4-billion-inflow-into-etfs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 00:39:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>周末袭击后以色列计划下一步行动 油价反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-21</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势，以及以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡与高级助手举行会议讨论对伊朗的下一次袭击，油价在上周暴跌近 8% 之后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-21</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 23:34:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
